// Haptic Teleoperation System with Force Feedback
// - Creates a haptic virtual environment with CHAI3D
// - Sends position data to server via SEND_PORT
// - Receives force feedback from server via RECV_PORT
// - Applies force feedback to the haptic device
//------------------------------------------------------------------------------
